{
  "texts": [
    "One is called the Automatic Prompt Engineer (APE) and the other is known as the Generated Knowledge Prompting (GKn).",
    "The APE starts out with one or several examples (of text, music, images, or anything else the model can work with) with the goal to ask the AI which prompts would work best to generate these (Zhou et al., 2023).",
    "This is helpful when we already know how a good response would look like but we do not know how to guide the model to this outcome.",
    "An example would be: \"Here is a love letter from a book that I like.",
    "I would like to write something similar to my partner but I don't know how."
  ]
}